Because this h1 is inside of the div, and

14
00:00:48.120 --> 00:00:51.000
I'm assuming that h1 has
nothing affecting it, right?

15
00:00:52.540 --> 00:00:53.710
This h1 will be blue.

16
00:00:53.710 --> 00:00:56.425
